| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1218 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8f40800c-c5b3-5c3c-b064-e7020d162b07"
